  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Peel and finely chop the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped shallot</strong> and <strong>meat-free mince</strong> to the pan and cook for 5-6 min<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>or until the mince is browned, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
